data.description: Great 1/2-acre lot that feels larger. Includes Fruit orchard, large, fenced garden and lots of flowers, which make this more like a hobby farm, with even a small chicken coop.  All electric 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with large back deck. Carport, 2 car garage with shop and 1/2 bath. Also, a lean-to off of garage for more covered storage. Property is completely fenced for all your animal's safety. There is sewer, power and water hook up to a RV site next to garage.  So many features its a must see.  Within walking distance to all Troy has to offer.  This property has an assumable loan, at 3.375% for qualified buyers. Call Sharon S Denton, 406-291-6719, or your real estate professional.
